<p><b>REPORT FROM ST VINCENT DE PAUL</b>. Your donations
to the Third Sunday of the Month Collection for SVdP
allowed our Cathedral Vincentians to make 149 home
visits during April, May and June and help 195 low (or
no) income residents of St James Parish who struggle to
pay for life's necessities, such as rent, electricity, beds,
